# Intro

Like `top` but for open files.

# Installation

    sudo pip3 install oftop

# Usage

Call the programm:

    sudo oftop

Then you will see output like this:

    oftop v0.1.0 (Ctrl+C to quit)

      PID     USER STATUS   POSITION       SIZE   POS%      SPEED  COMMAND                   FILE
